            <h1 class="fw-bold mb-4">About TechHaven</h1>

            <p class="lead text-muted mb-4">
                Founded in 2018, TechHaven Electronics has grown from a small Oslo-based startup
                into one of Scandinavia's most trusted online electronics retailers.
            </p>

